episodes.title: Korea's Most Disturbing Cults Iceberg
episodes.description:
#korea #cult #horror 
Exploring the dark side of south korea cults,  this iceberg serves as a cult documentary, shining light on dangerous groups and their impact on korean culture. From shincheonji to other lesser-known sects, we'll **deep(or dark lol) dive** into the world of koreas unregulated religions and the dangers they pose, for anyone traveling to south korea.
